          </div>
          <div class="values">
            <h2>02</h2>
            <h3>discovery</h3>
            <p>when facing a new design, it's important to discover everything about it helping to build the best product for the right market</p>
          </div>
          <div class="values">
            <h2>03</h2>
            <h3>teamwork</h3>
            <p>if you want to create an amazing product, it's going to take a village. Working efficiently and checking in with teams keeps me focused on the task at hand</p>
          </div>
          <div class="values">
            <h2>04</h2>
            <h3>sense of ownership</h3>
            <p>i hit the peak of my creativity when inspired to try new things. By investing in my own work, I open doors and solve problems in new ways</p>
          </div>
          <div class="values">
            <h2>05</h2>
            <h3>self evaluation</h3>
            <p>no great designer improves without learning from experience. By evaluating and critiquing my own work, I continue to grow</p>
          </div>
          <div class="values">
            <h2>06</h2>
            <h3>continuous learning</h3>
            <p>by seeking out ways to improve my creativity and skillset, I stay up to date with trends and never stagnant</p>
